snippet.title: Fortnite Season 6 Battle Pass - Now with Pets!
snippet.description:
Details at http://fortnite.com/Battle-Pass

100 tiers. Over 100 rewards. Still 950 V-Bucks! 

Level up your Battle Pass to unlock Bonesy, Scales, and Camo, new critters that will join you on your journey across the map. These passive companions are always by your side, reacting to different situations you find yourself in.

Play Fortnite Battle Royale, the completely free 100-player PvP mode. One giant map, A Battle Bus, Last one standing wins. ESRB Rating: Teen with Violence.
